Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cpf": "{{cpf}}",
  "scarabId": "{{scarabId}}",
  "recommendLogic": "PERSONAL",
  "limit": 20,
  "includeCategories": ["WOMEN>Coats & Jackets"],
  "excludeItems": ["2540"],
  "timeout": 45000,
  "headless": true,
  "useCache": false
}

###
### CPF sin formato (solo números)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scraping/recommendations/cpf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cpf": "12345678900",
  "scarabId": "{{scarabId}}",
  "recommendLogic": "PERSONAL",
  "limit": 10,
  "headless": true
}

###
### Verificar estado del job
